<br>
If MobHP &lt; RainDamage then Resist.<br>
<br>
So if a mob has EXACTLY 630hp left, for example, then Sirocco does still go through, and you get a kill shot. Explains the extreme rarity (1 in 630 chance in this case), and also shows the Rain spell corpse poof bug is probably fixed.<br>
<br>
